# Web3Forms access key — powers the contact form (leads are emailed to Gmail).
# Create a free key at https://web3forms.com (enter the destination email; no login).
# Copy this file to .env.local and paste your key. .env.local is gitignored.
# In production, set the same variable in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# If this is unset, the form still "works" by showing a client-side success state
# (no email is sent) — handy for local dev and CI builds.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
